{"sn2.17:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.17 ","sn2.17:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.17:0.3":"Subrahmasutta ","sn2.17:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho subrahma devaputto bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.17:2.1":"“Niccam utrastamidam cittam, ","sn2.17:2.2":"niccam ubbiggamidam mano; ","sn2.17:2.3":"Anuppannesu kicchesu, ","sn2.17:2.4":"atho uppatitesu ca; ","sn2.17:2.5":"Sace atthi anutrastam, ","sn2.17:2.6":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”ti. ","sn2.17:3.1":"“Nannatra bojjha tapasa, ","sn2.17:3.2":"nannatrindriyasamvara; ","sn2.17:3.3":"Nannatra sabbanissagga, ","sn2.17:3.4":"sotthim passami paninan”ti. ","sn2.17:4.1":"Idamavoca …pe… ","sn2.17:4.2":"tatthevantaradhayiti. "}